          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_400698864424535336.png",
                "id": "talent99217",
                "key": "轰霆翼斩",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "轰霆翼斩"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>对附属有<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷鸣探知</span>的敌方角色造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。（如果敌方不存在符合条件角色，则改为对出战角色造成伤害）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/8e1f1486bab5fc117e480c06e923634b_2841698917929990375.png",
                "id": "talent52820",
                "key": "雷墙倾轧",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷墙倾轧"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">轰雷禁锢</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/71e8c31afa5e7b779c1b2604bccc7b1e_5510041120877212753.png",
                "id": "talent26670",
                "key": "轰雷禁锢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "轰雷禁锢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，在敌方场上生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷霆探针</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/7fcdf904a4d1623ab0a882884eb4c2e2_2861291437940820852.png",
                "id": "talent51492",
                "key": "雷霆探知",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷霆探知"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>对附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷鸣探知</span>的敌方角色造成造成3点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>。（如果敌方不存在符合条件角色，则改为对出战角色造成伤害）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_927960272452314642.png",
                "id": "talent15535",
                "key": "轰雷禁锢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/8fe464d5ca7b4e1ea4b17f6e7f5161fb_4047204636588287705.png",
                "title": "轰雷禁锢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4825193638978206458.png",
                "id": "talent76734",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷鸣探知</span></strong></p><p>此状态存在期间，可以触发1次：所附属角色受到雷音权现其召唤物成的伤害+1。</p><p>（同一方场上最多存在一个此状态。雷音权现的部分技能，会以所附属角色为目标。）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷霆探针</span></strong></p><p>所在阵营角色使用技能后：对所在阵营出战角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷鸣探知</span>。 （每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3619068889667815298.png",
